Distribution. The species was captured at 
<quantity id="4CF8E3CEFFF2FFE49F3F5E28FCECC314" box="[802,891,564,590]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" unit="m" value="1300.0">1300 m</quantity>
